videos.description: Klay Thompson explains that playing faster opened up shots for Steph Curry and breaks down the defensive approach against LeBron James.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Klay: Picking up pace benefits Warriors) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Klay: Picking up pace benefits Warriors

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith breaks down Kevin Durant's 26-point performance and how he matched up against LeBron James.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: KD played 'sensational game') 2018/06/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stephen A.: KD played 'sensational game'

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith says Ty Lue "needs to make some changes" including taking JR Smith out of the starting lineup.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A. says it's time to bench JR) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Stephen A. says it's time to bench JR

videos.description: JR Smith says he needs shoot better and play better defense than he did in Game 2. Smith also says he likes the attention he received from Warriors fans.
videos.headline: JR calls Game 2 performance 'terrible'

videos.description: Steve Kerr explains how much better the Warriors defended LeBron James in their Game 2 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Kerr say Warriors tried to make LeBron uncomfortable) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Kerr say Warriors tried to make LeBron uncomfortable

videos.description: Tyronn Lue doesn't think the Oracle crowd got into JR Smith's head and he simply missed shots.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Lue says Cavs still 'have confidence in JR') 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Lue says Cavs still 'have confidence in JR'

videos.description: Tristan Thompson says he can't control the referees and takes exception to a question about feeling "helpless" against the Warriors.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Thompson says he's 'over' the referees) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Thompson says he's 'over' the referees

videos.description: Klay Thompson explains how he did not realize how much you use your ankles until you hurt it and Steph Curry says Klay could of turned to him.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Curry to Klay: 'Could of asked me' about ankle injuries) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Curry to Klay: 'Could of asked me' about ankle injuries

videos.description: LeBron James discusses how the Warriors defended him and says the odds being stacked against him are nothing new.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (LeBron: 'I think I got tired once') 2018/06/03

videos.headline: LeBron: 'I think I got tired once'

videos.description: Draymond Green tells a reporter that he can have his suit shorts as he won't have a need for them the rest of the Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Draymond shares where he got the idea for suit shorts) 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Draymond shares where he got the idea for suit shorts

videos.description: Steph Curry explains how much setting an NBA Finals record for most 3-pointers means to him after the adversity he faced this season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Curry on Finals record: 'It's a pretty cool deal') 2018/06/03

videos.headline: Curry on Finals record: 'It's a pretty cool deal'

videos.description: Draymond Green gives props to his designer and stylist and says the only reason he likes his suit shorts is because sometimes it gets hot.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Draymond says his shorts weren't to psych out his opponent) 2018/06/3

videos.headline: Draymond says his shorts weren't to psych out his opponent
